Enum Class SudokuSize

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SudokuSize>
sudoku.enums.SudokuSize
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SudokuSize>, Constable
public enum SudokuSize extends Enum<SudokuSize>
The `SudokuSize` enum represents the size of the Sudoku. It contains the different sizes of the Sudoku. It allows to choose the size of the Sudoku.
